$BORRADO_TABLAS
  Filter [ZBPC]
  For [ZBPC]
    Delete [ZBPC]
  Next
  Filter [ZBPC]

  Filter [ZAPU]
  For [ZAPU]
    Delete [ZAPU]
  Next
  Filter [ZAPU]

  Filter [ZCGE]
  For [ZCGE]
    Delete [ZCGE]
  Next
  Filter [ZCGE]

  Filter [ZDIR]
  For [ZDIR]
    Delete [ZDIR]
  Next
  Filter [ZDIR]
Return

